{
  "texts": [
    "By engaging in dialogues with the tutor bot, learners actively constructed their understanding, consolidated information, and developed well-structured summaries.",
    "This process not only facilitated the acquisition of new knowledge but also fostered critical analysis and the integration of information.",
    "It is important to acknowledge that this study was conducted within the specific context of postgraduate education reform and development classes at the Education University of Hong Kong.",
    "Consequently, the generalizability of the findings to other educational contexts may be limited.",
    "Additionally, the study participants had an average level of graduate education, and the extent to which the tutor bot can accommodate learners with more varying or diversified educational backgrounds remains unexplored."
  ]
}